{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497930/extras/Gambagun-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1738792207\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gamba Gun</strong> is the <i>idiotic</i> fusion of <strong>top-down shooter</strong> and <strong>deck building </strong>rogue-likes. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THIS AIN'T NO BABY GAME FOR BABIES! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Gamba Gun</strong>, your weapons are slot machines, and <i>you must gamble your life</i>. The recipe to success is 100% skill, 100% decision-making, and <i>1000% dumb luck! </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(That's <strong>1100% More</strong> per 100%!) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">((\u1d1b\u029c\u1d00\u1d1b's <strong>12x</strong> \u1d20\u1d00\u029f\u1d1c\u1d07!)) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497930/extras/GambagunGameplayGif-ezgif.com-crop_1_.gif?t=1738792207\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">IT'S TWO GUNS, </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wield dual revolvers that have the special capacity to fire nonsensical ammunition. <i>Oh yeah</i>, every time you reload them, <i>their ammo magically shuffles.</i> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A BUNCH OF BULLETS, </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experiment with endless ammo combinations, and fill your guns with the best bullets to create powerful synergies! Be careful when choosing, because the bullets in your clip can synergize to destroy enemies, or you... . .. .\u00a0 . .. . .\u00a0 . ..\u00a0 .. . .. .. \u00a0\u00a0 .. .. .\u00a0 . ..\u00a0 .. ..\u00a0 .. . . .\u00a0 . .. \u00a0\u00a0 .. .. .\u00a0 . . ..\u00a0 .. .</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">AND BAD GUYS TOO. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fend off a wide cast of colorful cartoon characters that will just as quickly die as they can kill you. Survive as many waves as you can as the surrounding foes become increasingly absurd.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unique Features: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>RGB:</strong> Gamba Gun uses the RGB Color Model. Wow, that's over <strong>Sixteen-Million*</strong> colors!<strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>*</strong>\u0262\u1d00\u1d0d\u0299\u1d00 \u0262\u1d1c\u0274 \u1d05\u1d0f\u1d07s \u0274\u1d0f\u1d1b \u1d04\u1d0f\u0274\u1d1b\u1d00\u026a\u0274 \u1d1b\u029c\u1d00\u1d1b \u1d0d\u1d00\u0274\u028f \u1d04\u1d0f\u029f\u1d0f\u0280s </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>OST:</strong> Gamba Gun has an original soundtrack, so <strong>you basically get an album*</strong> too. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>*</strong>\u0274\u1d0f\u1d1b \u0274\u1d07\u1d04\u1d07ss\u1d00\u0280\u026a\u029f\u028f \u1d07\u0274\u1d0a\u1d0f\u028f\u1d00\u0299\u029f\u1d07 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Settings Menu:</strong> Using computer*, you can now change things. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*\u1d04\u1d0f\u1d0d\u1d18\u1d1c\u1d1b\u1d07\u0280 \u0274\u1d0f\u1d1b \u026a\u0274\u1d04\u029f\u1d1c\u1d05\u1d07\u1d05 </p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3497930?t=1738792207","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3497930?t=1738792207","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497930/ef064960f60f4700d3fac42de89b1049da360955/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738792207","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497930/ef064960f60f4700d3fac42de89b1049da360955/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738792207","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497930/extras/Gambagun-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1738792207\" /></p><